  <brief_title>Sodium Restriction in the Management of Cirrhotic Ascites</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Efficacy of 2 Gram Versus 4 Gram Sodium Restriction in the Management of Cirrhotic Ascites</official_title>
  <sponsors>
